</div></div></section></section><section id="floats-group1" class="floats-group"><section class="bt xbox font-sm" id="BX1"><h2 class="obj_head">Highlights.</h2>
<ul id="L3" class="list" style="list-style-type:disc">
<li><p id="P58">We extend GIST for quantifying population representativeness of
related studies</p></li>
<li><p id="P59">We contribute a method for iteratively characterizing
underrepresented patients</p></li>
<li><p id="P60">We demonstrated the value of this method using Type 2 diabetes
mellitus studies</p></li>
<li><p id="P61">Our study confirms knowledge in literature and can generalize to
other diseases</p></li>
</ul></section></section><section id="S30" class="ack"><h2 class="pmc_sec_title">Acknowledgments</h2>
